---
// Hero.astro - A hero section component with diagonal split design
---

<section class="hero-container">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Especialistas em otimizar operações e maximizar lucros através do ERP Sankhya.</h1>
      <button class="cta-button">Solicite uma demonstração</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-container {
    position: relative;
    height: 500px;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-image: url('/images/business-person.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center right;
  }

  .hero-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 55%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #0047AB; /* Royal blue color */
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 85% 100%, 0 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-text {
    width: 50%;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-text h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    background-color: #E6A817; /* Gold color for the button */
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #D69915;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-container::before {
      width: 100%;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 60%, 0 100%);
    }

    .hero-text {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>